FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://coala.ip/

# coalaip api

## Works Collection [/works]

### List All Works [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "name": "Lord of the Rings"
            }
        ]

### Create a New Work [POST]

You may create your own work using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a work.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "Lord of the Rings"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /works/2

    + Body

            {
                "name": "Lord of the Rings",
                "txid": "1234567890"
            }
            

