## Rights Collection [/rights]

### List All Rights [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "name": "Lord of the Rings"
            }
        ]

### Create a New Right [POST]

You may create your own right using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a right.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "creation": "https://coala.ip/creations/123",
            "usageType": ["copy", "play"]
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /rights/123

    + Body

            {
                "creation": "https://coala.ip/creations/123",
                "usageType": ["copy", "play"],
                "url": ""https://coala.ip/rights/123"";
            }



